description: EtherLite (ETL) is a token built on the ERC20 protocol of Ethereum. It is fully secure and limited. There are 100,000 ETL in circulation. Each token is distributed as Airdrop and Bounty. EtherLite is a simpler version of Litecoin integrated in the Ethereum blockchain. Its benefits are endless among the speed of execution of contracts and its growth prospects.
name: EtherLite
